query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_entries,
  SUM(durationHours) / 100 as total_hours,
  MIN(date) as earliest_date,
  MAX(date) as latest_date
FROM timeEntries 
WHERE userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE openId LIKE '%vikram%' LIMIT 1)
  AND date >= '2025-10-01' 
  AND date < '2025-11-01';
